    <Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}">
        GridDataControl - Summaries
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        A Grid Data Control can display summaries based on the bound data. Here are some samples that demonstrate summary features of the GridDataControl. 
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Basic Summaries Demo</Bold>- This sample uses the GridDataControl to show summaries for simple groups.
    </Paragraph>
	    
    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Custom Summaries Demo</Bold> - This sample uses the GridDataControl to calculate and display custom aggregate summaries.
    </Paragraph>
    
    <Paragraph>
        <Bold>Table Summaries Demo</Bold>- This sample shows adding summaries to the Table as frozen rows.
    </Paragraph>
	
	<Paragraph>
        <Bold>Sort by Summary Demo</Bold>- This samples demonstrates how to sort groups by the value of a summary.
    </Paragraph>
